BOARD OF DIRECTORS

Between 1999 and 2004 he served as Executive Director and Group Managing Director (Commercial) of Seksun Corporation Ltd, which was then listed on the Main Board of the Singapore Exchange (”SGX). He later held non- executive directorships in several other SGX listed companies.
